	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />after trying and trying i cant get accurate emu when two sprites overlap,
<br />the thing is funny in my emu: its like one sprite fights to the other one, i mean its timed, one time you see in front of the other and viceversa
<br />
<br />any idea what could be the problem?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
